The paper deals with virtualization in wireless communication systems, which is a topic that falls under the category of computer networks and the sub-category of network architecture and design. Therefore, cs.NI (Networks and Internet Architecture) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves information theory and system theory, which are covered in cs.IT (Information Theory) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper discusses resource allocation and representation level, which are related to distributed computing and computer architecture, respectively, and hence cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.COM (Computer Architecture) are also possible sub-categories.
